---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Meet Zak Winnick, your Northern California-based Fora travel advisor specializing in adventure travel with comfort and intention."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-sage-50">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sage-600 font-medium mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">About Wyld Wandering</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-semibold text-stone-900 leading-tight">
          Adventure with intention.<br />
          <span class="text-sage-600">Comfort by design.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-stone-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          I'm Zak Winnick, a Northern California-based certified Fora travel advisor who believes the best adventures
          don't require sacrificing comfort or spontaneity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Personal Story Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-6">
            My Journey
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              My path to travel advising wasn't conventional. I spent years in the tech industry, solving complex problems
              and learning that the best solutions come from understanding what people actually need, not just what they
              think they want.
            </p>
            <p>
              Before that, I worked in luxury hospitality, where I discovered my passion for creating memorable experiences.
              I learned the art of anticipating needs, the importance of those small details that transform a good trip into
              an unforgettable one, and the difference that genuine care makes in someone's experience.
            </p>
            <p>
              These two worlds shaped how I approach travel planning today: with technical precision and heartfelt attention
              to what matters most to each traveler.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-sand-100 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12">
          <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-display text-stone-800 leading-relaxed">
            "The best trips aren't about checking boxes. They're about finding those unexpected moments that stay with you long after you've unpacked."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="mt-6 text-sage-600 font-medium">- Zak Winnick</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-6">
          The Wyld Wandering Philosophy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
          I believe adventure and comfort aren't opposites. They're dance partners.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 4m0 13V4m0 0L9 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Rugged, Not Rough</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            You can explore a slot canyon at sunrise and still return to a hot shower and a proper bed.
            Adventure doesn't mean discomfort.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Intentional Design</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            Every element of your trip should serve a purpose. I focus on thoughtful itineraries that balance
            exploration with restoration.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Personal Connection</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            I take the time to understand how you travel, what excites you, and what recharges you.
            Your trip should feel like yours.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Credentials Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="bg-sage-50 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sage-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-sage-600 font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Certified</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-stone-900">Fora Travel Advisor</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
              As a Fora travel advisor, I have access to exclusive perks, upgrades, and insider knowledge
              that can transform your trip. From complimentary breakfast and room upgrades to special
              amenities and VIP treatment, I leverage these partnerships to add extra value to every journey I plan.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-6">
            Professional Credentials
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              I partnered with Fora because they share my belief that travel should be personal,
              not transactional. Their platform gives me the tools and relationships to deliver
              exceptional experiences while maintaining the personal touch that makes travel planning meaningful.
            </p>
            <p>
              Being a Fora advisor means I'm continuously learning, connected to a community of
              passionate travel professionals, and equipped with the resources to handle anything
              from simple getaways to complex multi-destination adventures.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Travel Style Section -->
  <section class="bg-stone-900 text-white">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-semibold mb-6">
          What Gets Me Out There
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
          When I'm not planning adventures for others, here's where you'll find me.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Off-Roading</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">
            Dirt roads, rocky trails, and the freedom to explore beyond the pavement.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-stone-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Overlanding</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">
            Self-reliant travel through remote landscapes, camping under the stars.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-stone-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Desert Exploration</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">
            The stark beauty of wide-open spaces and ancient landscapes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-stone-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Redwood Forests</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">
            Towering giants and misty trails in my Northern California backyard.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-stone-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          I appreciate boutique hotels that feel like discoveries, thoughtfully designed cabins tucked away from the crowds,
          and well-equipped campsites where you can enjoy nature without sacrificing a hot shower.
          If this resonates with how you like to travel, we'll get along just fine.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-sage-600">
    <div class="container-wide section-padding text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-6">
        Ready to Plan Your Next Adventure?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-sage-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Whether you're dreaming of coastal road trips, desert expeditions, or mountain retreats,
        I'd love to help you design a journey that fits your style.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href={`${baseUrl}contact`}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-sage-700 font-semibold rounded-md hover:bg-stone-100 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Let's Talk
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href={`${baseUrl}services`}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold rounded-md hover:bg-sage-700 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          View Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
